Corporate lawyer (Singapore qualified), 3 to 5 years PQE
Location:  Singapore
A rare and exciting opportunity for a top quality Singapore qualified Associate to join a premier firm with expansion plans and a focus on high end cross-border transactions.
You will be joining a team of heavyweight partners with broad M&A, joint ventures, and regulatory experience in the ASEAN region, and the successful candidate with have the benefit of exposure to this workload.
You must either be practicing at an international firm or top tier local firm Corporate practice, have a minimum 2:1 or equivalent degree, and confident “can-do” personality. You will be rewarded with a market leading salary in return.
Please contact Fred dos Santos at JLegal in Singapore on +65 6818 9701 or submit your resume to fred quoting Ref no: FDS-PS-1397
